# Domain Layer

Zero dependencies on other projects. Entities inherit `BaseEntity`. Events inherit `BaseEvent`, raised via `AddDomainEvent()`.

Structure: `Common/`, `Constants/`, `Entities/`, `Enums/`, `Events/`, `Exceptions/`, `Interfaces/`, `ValueObjects/`.

Define repository/service interfaces here; Infrastructure implements them.
